B. Explorer.MontiAI.com – The Sovereign Interface

· Frontend Portal: The exclusive web dashboard where authorized humans interact with the AI.
· Features:
  · Real-time query execution.
  · Visual ledger explorer (view your interaction history).
  · Premium model selection (BYOM, DeepSeek, Qwen).
  · Private "Human-in-the-Loop" controls (allowing humans to manually correct or retrain the AI).

C. Private Ledger for AI Algorithm (The Monti Neural Ledger)

· Structure: A distributed, immutable hash-chain ledger (built on a private, permissioned DAG) stored on your Termux/backend infrastructure.
· Function:
  · Every human-AI interaction (prompt, response, correction, and feedback) is cryptographically hashed and stored on the ledger.
  · The ledger is only accessible by IAM MONTI and explicitly authorized wallet addresses.
  · This ledger serves as the training ground—the AI algorithm continuously refines its behavior based on the ledger's human-interaction data, without leaking any private context to the public.

